snippet.title: Now, Indians to visit Pakistan for proof that Jaish attacked Pathankot

localized.description:
India will send a team of investigators to Pakistan to collect evidence that January's deadly attack on the Pathankot's air force base was the work of terror group Jaish-e-Mohammed and its chief, Masood Azhar. Sources told NDTV that the date for the visit to Pakistan has not been fixed yet.
